==English==

===Etymology===
[[devil]] + [[-ish]]

===Adjective===
'''devilish'''

# Resembling or characteristic of a [[devil]].
#: ''A devilish grin.''
# (''informal'') Extreme.
#: ''Devilishly good.''

====Synonyms====
#(1) [[demonic]], [[diabolic]], [[diabolical]]

